content:
**The goal for this sprint 1 :**

*   Create and familiarize yourself with the docker container.
*   Since no data from the taiga integration team pull data using taiga API
*   Convert data to Json for frontend team
*   Write unit test cases to have a minimum of 70% code coverage.
content_html:
The goal for this sprint 1 :

  • Create and familiarize yourself with the docker container.
  • Since no data from the taiga integration team pull data using taiga API
  • Convert data to Json for frontend team
  • Write unit test cases to have a minimum of 70% code coverage.

content:
**Sprint Retrospective:**

*   As per planning, we were able to complete all the tasks and deploy the container.
*   Was not able to integrate with the front-end team.
*   Had a slow start and could have saved some time with the learning process.
*   Did not implement TDD or pair-wise programming will try to feature one of them in the next sprint.
